    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >泰坦空间站是一个复古科幻风的第一人称解密单人游戏</h2>在遥远的未来，1999年，一个叫大卫的系统操作员，为了逃避他的各种困难，决定接受一个宇宙空间站的工作。当他来到的时候，他平庸的工作在他发现后惊人的秘密后变得非常复杂。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >通过接受独立加油站的工作来逃避你的麻烦</h2>泰坦空间站和木星的月亮通过一个电梯和管道系统连接<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881120/extras/83b96e137c044f96c7faf22b4c7d1c9a.poster.avif?t=1700761406\" width=516 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881120/extras/83b96e137c044f96c7faf22b4c7d1c9a.webm?t=1700761406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881120/extras/83b96e137c044f96c7faf22b4c7d1c9a.mp4?t=1700761406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >和对讲机对话</h2>和其他人通过对讲机交流，但是你可以相信谁呢？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881120/extras/93c096250c26ee33f9b78fdc2fb4943f.poster.avif?t=1700761406\" width=516 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881120/extras/93c096250c26ee33f9b78fdc2fb4943f.webm?t=1700761406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881120/extras/93c096250c26ee33f9b78fdc2fb4943f.mp4?t=1700761406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >使用复古电脑</h2>连接到网络从而发现真相<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881120/extras/98e872e7f64b840dc734c3c7bf8ecaf4.poster.avif?t=1700761406\" width=516 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881120/extras/98e872e7f64b840dc734c3c7bf8ecaf4.webm?t=1700761406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881120/extras/98e872e7f64b840dc734c3c7bf8ecaf4.mp4?t=1700761406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >进入网络空间</h2>绝境之中需要特殊的解决方法<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881120/extras/19d63fa899c0c7838c9c9948218f79bd.poster.avif?t=1700761406\" width=516 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881120/extras/19d63fa899c0c7838c9c9948218f79bd.webm?t=1700761406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881120/extras/19d63fa899c0c7838c9c9948218f79bd.mp4?t=1700761406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一个故事性的冒险</h2>泰坦空间站需要3-4个小时去完成<br><br>这个游戏没有战斗<br>少量解密，游戏简单的一部分<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >个人开发者</h2>泰坦空间站是由Joakim Larsen一个人通过虚幻引擎开发的，他曾在超杀‘行尸走肉’游戏中担任3D设计师",
